caption.body: Maxim Zhestkov presents a series of experiments with black and white spheres in confined spaces to express laws of nature and demonstrate that all matter is composed of simple elements in complex arrangements and relationships. See "Elements" by Maxim Zhestkov, now playing in the Video Arts gallery, located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2PH9uhO
